<SLUG> BC-FBI-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MANY SNITCHES STILL DOING CRIME 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By DENNIS WAGNER AND PAT FLANNERY 
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
