<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-27 17:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0106 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-COX-GOP-VIRGINIA-0228     02-27 0659
