r l BC-LEAH-PERSONALS-SFCHRO     02-27 0813
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LEAH-PERSONALS-SFCHRON </SLUG>
  
 By LEAH GARCHIK  
 Copyright 2000 Chronicle Publishing Company 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
