   0228 CLOUD COVER -- 15p x 1 7/8 -- Predicted cloud cover each
day.
</P>
<P>
   0228 MOON PHASES -- 1 x 5/8 -- The phases of the moon.
</P>
<P>
   0228 EXTENDED FORECAST --Predicted weather for later in the
week.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
