   &UR; BUSINESS DAY _ (Moved in ``f'' category)  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   AIRPLANE-COMFORT (Undated) _ Passengers flying in coach may soon
find they have more room _ if they can get seats. American Airlines
is adding space between coach seats for those paying full fares,
and others, including British Airways and United, are segmenting
economy class into premium coach and true budget service. By David
J. Morrow.
</P>
